Class UserServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.neu.prattle.service.user.UserServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UserService

    public class UserServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements UserService
    Implementation of UserService It stores the user accounts in-memory, which means any user accounts created will be deleted once the application has been restarted.

    dated 2019-10-06
    Author:
